<Layout title="Butterfly - Projects - Zain Mobarik">
  <h1>Butterfly</h1>
  <p class="author">Social media app created from scratch pre-GPT</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
    <div style="position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; aspect-ratio: 16/9;">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/72qiclDGeTE"
        title="Butterfly YC Application Video"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        allowfullscreen
        style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0;">
      </iframe>
    </div>
    <p style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">YC Application Video (S23)</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Overview</h2>

  <p>We thought we were the next zuck, we thought we needed to bring the OG facebook back. It was an insanely fun ride, people loved the app but the stickness just wasn't there</p>

  <h2>Traction</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>30,000+ Downloads</strong> - Achieved substantial user adoption through organic growth and word-of-mouth</li>
    <li><strong>NatWest Accelerator</strong> - Selected for prestigious banking accelerator program</li>
    <li><strong>Angel Investment</strong> - Successfully secured funding from 2 angel investors</li>
    <li><strong>Pre-AI Development</strong> - Built entirely through manual coding and human ingenuity - I know, crazy times</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>The tech</h2>

  <p>Developing Butterfly required building every component from the ground up - from user authentication systems to real-time messaging, content feeds, and social interaction features. The project showcased full-stack development capabilities across mobile and backend systems.</p>

  <h2>Recognition</h2>

  <p>Being accepted into the NatWest Accelerator program provided access to mentorship, resources, and networking opportunities with other high-potential startups. The angel investment further validated the business model and growth potential.</p>

  <h2>Press Coverage</h2>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
